# Wardrobe Label Print Server Configuration

This file contains environment variables for the application.
# IMPORTANT: Use WLPS_ namespace prefix to avoid conflicts with other projects

## Database Configuration (Namespaced with WLPS_ prefix)
WLPS_DB_SERVER=your-sql-server
WLPS_DB_DATABASE=your-database-name
WLPS_DB_USERNAME=your-database-user
WLPS_DB_PASSWORD=your-secure-password
WLPS_DB_ENCRYPT=false
WLPS_DB_TRUST_CERT=true
WLPS_DB_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=30000

## Printer Configuration
PRINTER_IP=printerIP
PRINTER_PORT=9100

## Application Configuration
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=info
POLLING_INTERVAL=5000

## Notes
- POLLING_INTERVAL is in milliseconds (default: 5000ms = 5 seconds)
- Change LOG_LEVEL to 'debug' for more verbose logging
- For production, set NODE_ENV=production
